column2: SELECT  SpecObjAll.plate, SpecObjAll.mjd, SpecObjAll.fiberID, SpecObjAll.z, GalSpecLine.h_alpha_flux, GalSpecLine.h_beta_flux  FROM SpecObjAll JOIN GalSpecLine ON  SpecObjAll.specobjid = GalSpecLine.specobjid WHERE  h_alpha_flux > #*h_beta_flux AND SpecObjAll.class = &&& AND SpecObjAll.z between # and #  AND SpecObjAll.sn1_g >#
